{"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/MockServiceReference","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/RevenueCatPaywallService"],"anchor":"Related-Documentation","title":"Related Documentation"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/MockServiceReference","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/UIComponentsReference"],"anchor":"Reference","title":"Reference","generated":true}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/servicereference"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/ServiceReference"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","title":"Service Reference","modules":[{"name":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}],"role":"article"},"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"API reference for "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RevenueCatPaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" — the RevenueCat-backed "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" conformer that the paywall plugin consumes."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"RevenueCatPaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" adapts "},{"code":"RevenueCat.Purchases","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to the "},{"code":"PaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol that "},{"code":"SwiduxPaywall.PaywallPlugin","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" requires. It does one job: translate "},{"code":"CustomerInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" into "},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" (defined by "},{"code":"SwiduxPaywall","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") so the plugin can drive its state. Configuration of the RevenueCat SDK itself remains the caller’s responsibility."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For a step-by-step integration walkthrough, see "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService"},{"type":"text","text":". For the entitlement-mapping rules, see "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Library-target","text":"Library target"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Product: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Import: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"import SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"Package.swift","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":[".product(name: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\", package: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\"),"]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Types","text":"Types"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"docSwiduxRevenueCatPaywalldocumentationSwiduxRevenueCatPaywallRevenueCatPaywallService","text":"``doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/RevenueCatPaywallService``"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["public struct RevenueCatPaywallService: PaywallService {","    public init(","        entitlementID: String,","        permanentLicenseEntitlementID: String? = nil","    )","","    public func customerInfo() async throws -> EntitlementSnapshot","    public func customerInfoStream() -> AsyncStream<EntitlementSnapshot>","    public func restorePurchases() async throws -> EntitlementSnapshot","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Value type. Holds two "},{"code":"String","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" identifiers and forwards every call to "},{"code":"Purchases.shared","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". Safe to construct freely; cheap to pass into "},{"code":"PaywallPlugin","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"Initializer","text":"Initializer"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["public init(","    entitlementID: String,","    permanentLicenseEntitlementID: String? = nil",")"]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"entitlementID"},{"type":"text","text":" — RevenueCat entitlement identifier that grants pro access. Surfaces as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"EntitlementSnapshot.isPro"},{"type":"text","text":" when active."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"permanentLicenseEntitlementID"},{"type":"text","text":" — Optional secondary identifier for a lifetime \/ permanent entitlement. Surfaces as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"EntitlementSnapshot.hasPermanentLicense"},{"type":"text","text":" when active. Pass "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" if the app has no separate lifetime SKU."}]}]}]},{"name":"Important","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Purchases.configure(withAPIKey:)"},{"type":"text","text":" before constructing the service. The service does not configure RevenueCat itself, and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Purchases.shared"},{"type":"text","text":" traps if used unconfigured."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"important"},{"level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"customerInfo-async-throws-%3E-EntitlementSnapshot","text":"`customerInfo() async throws -> EntitlementSnapshot`"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"One-shot fetch. Calls "},{"code":"Purchases.shared.customerInfo()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and maps the result."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Throws whatever the RevenueCat SDK throws ("},{"code":"ErrorCode.networkError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":".offlineConnectionError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", etc.). The plugin catches the error and dispatches "},{"code":".refreshFailed(message)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"customerInfoStream-%3E-AsyncStream%3CEntitlementSnapshot%3E","text":"`customerInfoStream() -> AsyncStream<EntitlementSnapshot>`"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Long-lived stream. Wraps "},{"code":"Purchases.shared.customerInfoStream","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and yields a new "},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" for every change RevenueCat reports — purchase, refund, family-share update, sandbox renewal."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The stream finishes when the underlying RevenueCat stream finishes. The plugin’s "},{"code":".observeCustomerInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" effect normally keeps it alive for the duration of the session; cancel by cancelling the consuming "},{"code":"Task","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", which terminates the stream and tears down the bridge."}]},{"level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"restorePurchases-async-throws-%3E-EntitlementSnapshot","text":"`restorePurchases() async throws -> EntitlementSnapshot`"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Calls "},{"code":"Purchases.shared.restorePurchases()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and maps the result. Throws whatever the SDK throws on error."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The plugin’s "},{"code":".restorePurchases","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" action wraps this call and dispatches "},{"code":".customerInfoUpdated","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" on success or "},{"code":".refreshFailed","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" on error."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Entitlement-mapping","text":"Entitlement mapping"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For every "},{"code":"CustomerInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" the service receives:"}]},{"header":"row","type":"table","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configuration"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isPro"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"hasPermanentLicense"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"entitlementID"},{"type":"text","text":" active"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(next column)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"entitlementID"},{"type":"text","text":" inactive or missing"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(next column)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"permanentLicenseEntitlementID == nil"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"—"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"permanentLicenseEntitlementID"},{"type":"text","text":" active"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"—"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"permanentLicenseEntitlementID"},{"type":"text","text":" inactive or missing"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"—"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Both flags are checked independently against the same "},{"code":"CustomerInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". A user with both active subscription and lifetime entitlements gets both flags set. See "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping"},{"type":"text","text":" for the reasoning behind the truth table."}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"]]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/MockServiceReference":{"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/mockservicereference","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"API reference for ","type":"text"},{"code":"MockRevenueCatPaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" — a controllable ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" conformer for previews and tests that does not touch ","type":"text"},{"code":"Purchases.shared","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/MockServiceReference","role":"article","title":"Mock Service Reference"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/UIComponentsReference":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywa